OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man has admitted exploiting a        
OL,6, vulnerable worker who was kept in a    
OL,7, freezing 6ft (2m) shed for 40 years.   
OL,9,FPeter Swailes, 56, denied conspiring to
OL,10,Ffacilitate travel of another with a    
OL,11,Fview to exploitation, but changed his  
OL,12,Fplea at Carlisle Crown Court.          
OL,14,FThe defendant's father, also Peter     
OL,15,FSwailes, 81, was accused of the same   
OL,16,Foffence but died in September 2021.    
OL,18,FThe Gangmasters and Labour Abuse       
OL,19,FAuthority (GLAA) said the case in      
OL,20,FCarlisle had been "traumatic".         
